name: One Pace
description: This integration is experimental because the One Pace project currently does not expose metadata in a stable manner, so we have to rely on scraping data from the project website instead. Therefore, medatata retrieval might break spontaneously if the website changes.
overview: Metadata and cover art integration for the One Pace project
